subtasks.details:
Aktualisiere frontend/src/types/employee.ts:

**Employee Interface:**
```typescript
interface Employee {
  id: number;
  title?: string;
  first_name: string;
  last_name: string;
  position: string;
  email: string;
  birth_date?: string; // ISO date string
  date_hired: string; // ISO date string
  federal_state: FederalState;
  active: boolean;
  created_at: string;
  updated_at: string;
}
```

**VacationAllowance Interface:**
```typescript
interface VacationAllowance {
  id: number;
  employee_id: number;
  year: number;
  annual_allowance: number;
  carryover_days: number;
  total_allowance: number;
  created_at: string;
  updated_at: string;
}
```

**FederalState Enum:**
```typescript
enum FederalState {
  BW = 'Baden-Württemberg',
  BY = 'Bayern',
  // ... alle 16 Bundesländer
}
```

**Form Interfaces:**
- EmployeeCreateForm, EmployeeUpdateForm
- VacationAllowanceForm

**API Response Types:**
- EmployeeWithVacation = Employee & { vacation_allowances: VacationAllowance[] }
